-- V35 — default MATERIAL positions per trade (~295). The default catalog was
-- 100% WORK (a labour reference); this adds the common materials a master lists in a
-- client estimate — with orientative market prices (rabotniki/Epicentr-grounded; some
-- are market estimates the master corrects, same as V31 prices). type='MATERIAL',
-- added_in_version=3 so existing masters get them via "Add new from library" and fresh
-- registrations get them seeded. Trades already use the DB enum codes.
